Good Morning Family!! I am praying for you this morning. I believe today is going to be your day for turnarounds and breakthroughs. If you are waking up and already dreading your day, it's a sign that you probably need to do some summer cleaning in your space. Life is hard all by itself.. you don't need the wrong people involved in your world adding to it. I want you to go find yourself a mirror and begin telling yourself just how awesome you are! That you're victorious. That you're taking back everything the devil has stolen. That you're not pitiful, but powerful! As long as you have a pulse, God's not done! Happiness is a choice... and it's your CHOICE! Keep your heart in order. Pay attention to who you are allowing in your ear today. If they are gossiping, spewing doubt and unbelief. They are pollution to your destiny. Move them from your VIP section of life and to the balcony.. tell them to watch you from a distance. Doesn't mean you don't love them, but it means you gotta love you enough to surround yourself with likeminded people who are moving with the vibe of where you want to be! You aren't stuck... unless you want to be! You're the CEO of your life.. you are in charge of keeping your space free! Now, go have a great day. Hustle so much that people don't have to ask your name! 👊🏼👊🏼 you RAWK!!! #reatalkkim #grateful #life #greatpeople #greatday #freedom #friends #excited #destiny #hope #big #favor #god

🌸 Beauty begins the moment you decide to be yourself 🌸

One of the best kept secrets is the fact that beauty begins the moment you decide to be yourself. There is nothing beautiful about someone who is fake or artificial, even if they look gorgeous on the outside. If you want others to see the real you and to recognize the inner beauty that we all have then you have to be yourself and not try to be someone that you are not. As soon as you do this others will start to notice you and see the person that you are instead of the phony that you are trying to be. When you try to be someone that you are not all you will do is make yourself unhappy, and the people who surround you are not true friends. Instead you will always know that these people are only your friends because of who you are pretending to be, and once you stop pretending they will quickly fade into the woodwork and be gone 😘

When you are yourself others will quickly notice your confidence and see the inner good that you possess. This is true beauty, not some fake standard that magazines and celebrities hold out as perfection. If others like you for yourself then you know they will always be there for you through thick and thin. If people are only close to you because you always have flawless makeup and you wear the latest designer fashions then they will leave as soon as the good times end. If you want to be beautiful all you have to do is be yourself and you will shine with radiance ❤

Igår gick mitt hjärta i bitar 💔 Min gynekolog berättade att blodproverna visar att äggstockarna inte riktigt gör det dom ska, att dom påverkats av mina superstarka behandlingar. Jag hörde knappt hälften av vad hon sa, det bara susade i huvudet, men något om "det finns fortfarande möjlighet till äggdonator" och "du är inte riktigt i klimakteriet ännu" sen "du ska få en remiss till en fertilitetsläkare". Jag orkar inte. Mitt ljus i tunneln har vart att skaffa en liten knodd. Att korsa mina och min älskade Filips gener och skapa små troll med blå ögon! Men tydligen är chansen kraftigt reducerad även om hoppet INTE är ute. Hoppashoppas mina äggstockar repar sig på något vis. Men vet ni?! För första gången kan jag genuint glädjas av mina vänners graviditeter. Jag har lite innan sett det som att folk "försvinner" från det livet man hade tidigare med sena nätter och fest, men nu känner jag mig underbart glad för alla där ute som kan få barn. Det är verkligen en gåva som inte alla kan ta för givet. Och vet ni, det finns även massa barn som behöver en förälder där ute, det kanske inte alls blir blå ögon för min del. Men snälla GUDEN PÅ MOLNET åtminstone ett eget vill jag ha! Och först och främst: LÅT MIG FÅ LEVA TILLS JAG BLIR EN GAMMAL TANT I ROLIG HATT! 🙏🏼 Puss på alla magar och barn där ute! 💖✨ #hope #fuckcancer 💕👼🏼 I am heartbroken because my gynecologist told me my chance of having my own babies is reduced after all my strong treatments. There is still ha chance, even if it's small it's still there 🙏🏼 It feels very scary when a function in your body is "breaking down" and I hate that the cancer is trying to take away another thing from me. I really want my life and my health back now, and I'm hoping for own children. But Filip said we can travel around the world to find a baby, so I feel I have the right guy by my side 💖 Like @methecancerfighter said: if you can't have children - surround your life with them. So now I feel very happy that so many of my girlfriends are pregnant. To have your own children is a gift you can not take for granted 💖👼🏼 📷: @olofringmar
